## ⚠️ Important Disclaimer

### About These Notes
- These are **personal study notes** taken from Palo Alto Networks course materials
- They are **NOT official Palo Alto Networks documentation**
- They are created for **personal study and educational purposes**
- Use these as a **supplement**, not a replacement for official materials

### Accuracy & Completeness
- These notes are **accurate to the best of my understanding** at the time of writing
- However, cybersecurity evolves rapidly
- Always verify critical information with official sources
- For official guidance, refer to Palo Alto Networks documentation

### Use Cases
✅ **Good for:**
- Exam preparation (practice questions, memory tricks)
- Quick reference during studying
- Understanding key concepts
- Interview preparation

❌ **Not suitable for:**
- Production security implementation (use official docs)
- Critical security decisions (consult experts)
- Compliance documentation (use official sources)

